title: Use 10000 STREDIUM to promote our DAO
body:
# Authors
@juan

# Summary
This proposal is to use 10000 STREDIUM from the marketing wallet to promote our DAO with an airdrop campaign on Twitter to giveaway those tokens in order to interact with different proposals.
